{"tid":677182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：阿伯電梯仆親　保安飛身㩒掣救人","createTime":"2018-05-25T03:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T04:24:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2a21b834b95ff5dd681926a4b6b583bdd3e9660a","tid":677182,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:38:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180525/20401088\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180525%2F20401088&d=IzNnsw2NHj6Y0EKC5Yge5U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=0f128d0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180525%2F20401088&h=93811edb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180525/20401088</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月25日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：阿伯電梯仆親　保安飛身㩒掣救人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180525/large/1527181213_6bc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180525%2Flarge%2F1527181213_6bc5.jpg&h=e8907294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■伯伯成個人打橫趴電梯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意外有時候好難避免，特別係老人家，屋企人同街坊都應該打醒精神，好似順利邨呢位老伯搭電梯跌親，好彩有保安員同街坊發現，幫手報警。<br />\n<br />\n噚日中午12點幾，住喺秀茂坪順利邨嘅讀者黃先生行過商場，聽到有幾個人好大聲咁講嘢，<br />\n黃生就即刻跑去睇吓發生咩事啦！點知就見到一位老伯，喺扶手電梯跌低咗，成個人打橫趴咗喺度，額頭撞咗埋梯級，伯伯當時喺電梯嘅中段位置，保安員即刻飛身按緊急掣，將電梯煞停，而伯伯隨身物品銀包、電話，就碌晒落地。<br />\n<br />\n街坊驚伯伯傷到骨頭，都唔敢扶起佢，惟有等救護員到場。救護員幫佢包紮後，抬上救護車送院。據聞伯伯乘搭扶手電梯，行到一半嗰陣突然頭暈暈，「阿伯突然好似腳軟暈低，跣咗一兩級」。好彩救護員嚟到之後，伯伯慢慢醒番。警方回應話，姓劉嘅80歲老伯被送到去聯合醫院治理。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：罕有雙頭魚BB出世　主人：會盡力養大<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：拖頭跌鐵板　累紅隧大塞車"},{"pid":"78459cc42fbb7b664bfb0bc8f9aa8e3a6c4fd82d","tid":677182,"uid":34757,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a69441a4546d24e02469e1cec4f50c6d36a7dc8","tid":677182,"uid":1254,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"廢老連電梯都唔識搭"},{"pid":"403e54f4d07248b697f4978baeb5690db6a35725","tid":677182,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"咁都可以上新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b3b3777f47dc526e399c9f22e2bd8efb41f4d8","tid":677182,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07c604491615e44c33a4c42f9425cf93a683a673","tid":677182,"uid":185683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0d4f5284010b484952a4f8a579dcf0dd769821f","tid":677182,"uid":60341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"之前有張阿伯慢慢碌落樓梯gif，想睇返"},{"pid":"63bd412ea5cbd999d24eb410bcc065b68b10b6ad","tid":677182,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:17:51.000Z","msg":"嘩, 有人仆落電梯! 等我影相先"},{"pid":"11ecb18ca06dfde6909f0d0376f50a2ee42b1b28","tid":677182,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"入黎想睇個保安員飛身示意圖<br />\n點知純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16787ea6bb3dfc286e541df05a1cc6d1c2180438","tid":677182,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"保安哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f247cbea436c5dae8c269cbfdfea50534cc685af","tid":677182,"uid":50719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"如無急切必要，唔好亂郁傷者，今次做得幾好"}]}